name: Gold Plated Citrine Ring
description:
This ring is made from a gorgeous citrine stone.  This is the highest quality citrine, which is a bright orange color, and is brimming with shining crystals.  The edge of the stone has been gold plated, and it is set on a very sturdy, gold plated, adjustable ring.

The size of the stone measures approximately 1.5" wide.  Please note that each one of these stones varies slightly in size and shape, however they are all equally beautiful!

name: Gold Plated Amethyst Cluster Ring
description:
This ring is made using a gorgeous, deep purple piece of amethyst. The stone has been gold plated.

No two stones are exactly the same. This picture is representative of the typical look of the ring you will receive, however this is not the exact one you will get. Each amethyst cluster is one of a kind and made by nature, therefore no two stones are alike. You do have my guarantee however that each ring is equally beautiful!

The stone measures approximately 1" wide and is set on an adjustable ring.

name: Gold Aura Druzy Geode Necklace
description:
This necklace is made with the most stunning gold aura druzy geode!  The druzy crystals shimmer wonderfully in the light.  The stone has a titanium aura coating, giving it the rich gold color, and it has a pop of contrast from the neon yellow, genuine leather.

The stone is attached to a hand dip dyed cotton chord, which starts off as black on the ends, and gradates into a soft purple color in the center.  The closure on this piece is magnetic, so it's so easy to slip on and of.  

The necklace measures 18" long, and the stone is approximately 2.25" wide.  This is a one of a kind piece, so you will receive the exact necklace pictured.

name: Amethyst Point Bracelet
description: This bracelet is made with the most vibrant, purple amethyst points and thick bronze toned chain. This bracelet is simple, elegant, and naturally beautiful.

name: Rainbow Aura Quartz Bullet Necklace
description:
This necklace is made using a gorgeous rainbow aura quartz point, and a spent brass, 9mm bullet casing. Rainbow aura quartz is formed when a thin layer of titanium is bonded with clear quartz, resulting in the luminescent rainbow of colors you see here. 

The crystal bullet has been strung from a 30", thick, antique gold toned chain

name: Rainbow Aura Quartz Geode Bracelet
description:
This bracelet is made using three stunning, rainbow aura quartz geode stones.  The stones have pretty little pockets of druzy crystals that pick up the light nicely.

The chain is bronze toned, with a lobster clasp.

name: Stardust Cuff
description:
This particular piece is called "Stardust". It is made with snake embossed genuine leather which has been hand=painted.  It was then brushed with pyrite dust, and embellished with a titanium aura quartz point. All of these elements have come together to create a magical, attention grabbing piece.

Everything is set on brass, and the cuff measures 1.5" wide.

name: Moon Goddess Cuff
description:
Please note that each stone will vary from cuff to cuff.

This cuff, the latest from my newest collection, is made with jaw dropping amethyst, matte gold fishbone chain, and cream snake embossed leather. The amethyst is a pretty violet color, and has been gold plated around the edges. 

It is set on cream and tan, snake embossed leather, which has been embellished with gold fishbone chain, for the perfect mixture of natural beauty, modern elegance, and edge. 

The base for the cuff is brass and measures 1.5" wide. It is very pliable and will fit most wrists.

name: Python Necklace
description:
The python necklace is just like the Viper, except the leather has not been encased in plastic tubing.  This style is fun and bright, with a long titanium aura quartz stone fixed in copper, as the focal point, strung from neon pink, braided, genuine leather. Titanium aura quartz is made by bonding a thin layer of titanium with a quartz stone.  The result is an iridescent, rainbow finish.

The leather rope measures 18" long, and the the titanium aura point measures approximately 2" long.

name: Alie(N)ation Brass and Leather Spike Cuff
description:
This cuff is from the Alie(N)ation collection.  It is made with brass, ostrich print embossed leather, with an iridescent rainbow finish, and brass hardware with gold spikes.  This bracelet is definitely a statement piece, to say the least.

The cuff measures 1.5" wide and is very pliable, so it can be squeezed or pulled to fit almost any size wrist.

name: Gold Aura Quartz Necklace
description:
This necklace is made with stunning gold aura quartz stones!  Gold aura quartz has a vibrant, rich gold color, so it will liven up any outfit, but stay simple and elegant at the same time.

The stones are strung from an 18" copper chain.

name: Raw Amethyst Crystal Studs
description:
These studs are made with gorgeous, raw amethyst crystals. The stones are a pretty dark lavender shade, and have there own unique and individual character.

The stones measure approximately .75" wide and are set on surgical steel posts.

name: Genuine Turquoise and Amethyst Necklace
description:
This necklace is made from gorgeous, vibrant, genuine turquoise and amethyst.  The deep purple of the amethyst compliments the rich hues of green and turquoise, making this necklace bright and bold, but very simple and elegant.  

The stones are strung from an 18" gold plated chain.  the width of the pendant is approximately 2.5" long.

name: Meteor Ring with Peacock Ore
description:
This ring is made from a brilliant peacock ore stone, also known as chalcopyrite.  Peacock ore is cousins to pyrite, and is made up the most brilliant shades of blue, green, purple and gold.

This ring is simple, yet eye catching.  It is set on a gold plated adjustable ring base.  The stone measures approximately 1" wide.

name: Pyrite Druzy Studs
description:
You will absolutely love these Pyrite Druzy Studs!  The are classic, simple, elegant, and of course, made with real, natural stones.  The pyrite, also known as fool's gold is brimming with sparkling druzy crystals.  This is the kind of style that can be dressed up or down.

Studs measure approximately .5", or about 1cm wide.

name: Titanium Aura Quartz Necklace
description:
This necklace is made from a stunning titanium aura quartz stone.  Titanium aura quartz has a gorgeous, iridescent, rainbow color.  This piece is simple yet bold.  

The stone is strung from an 18" copper toned chain.

name: Amethyst Point Bullet Necklace
description:
This necklace is made using a pretty purple amethyst point and a spent 9mm brass bullet casing. The amethyst is a deep, dark, purple, contrasting against the distressed look of the spent bullet casing. These crystal bullet necklaces are major statement pieces and conversation starters.

It is strung from a 18" gold toned chain. The chain can be shortened at the buyers request.

name: Amazonite and Citrine Necklace
description:
This beautiful necklace is made with beautiful, natural amazonite.  Amazonite comes in natural shades of aqua and greenish blue.  The focal point of the necklace is a bright orange citrine point.  

The stones are strung from a thin, 18" gold plated chain.

name: Citrine Point Bracelet
description: This bracelet is made with the most vibrant, orange citrine points and thick bronze toned chain. This bracelet is simple, elegant, and naturally beautiful.

name: Bismuth Hoop Earrings
description:
These cool earrings are made from futuristic looking bismuth stones.  Bismuth are stones that are grown in a lab, that form unique geometric-like shapes, with iridescent, rainbow finishes.  These bismuth stones are hanging in the middle of gold plated hoops, creating a very Solar System kind of feel.

The stones measure approximately .75" wide and the hoops are 2" long.

name: Raw Black Tourmaline Ring
description:
Black tourmaline is so beautifully natural, yet simple.  This rich black, moody stone makes the perfect understated, yet eye-catching ring.  

The stone measures approximately 1" across and is set on a gold plated adjustable ring.

name: Rainbow Aura and Fresh Water Pearl Bracelet
description: You will love this bracelet made from a stunning mixture of rainbow aura quartz and iridescent rainbow fresh water pearls.  The link chain is made with copper, and compliments the rainbow finish on the pearls and stone perfectly.

name: Cobra Necklace
description:
The Cobra necklace is bright, bold, contemporary, and natural. It is made with hand dyed rope, which starts as purple on the ends and blends into a soft black in the center.  The rope is encased in clear, plastic tubing, and the focal point to the necklace is a large, raw agate druzy stone, which has been wrapped in neon yellow leather.  The ends of the rope have been wrapped in matching leather as well.  

The necklace measures 18" around, and will rest right below the collarbone.

name: Viper Necklace
description:
The viper necklace is made with neon pink, braided leather, encased in clear plastic tubing.  The focal point of the necklace is made with copper hardware, and a titanium aura quartz point.  This necklace is the perfect combo for the girl who loves natural, industrial, and contemporary elements.  

Each stone has its own unique shape, pattern and color combination.  Titanium aura quartz is made when a thin layer of titanium is bonded with quartz.  The result is an iridescent, rainbow finish.

The necklace measures 18" around, so the pendant rests below the collarbone.

name: Rainbow Aura Quartz Point Necklace
description:
This gorgeous necklace is made using five stunning, rainbow aura quartz points.  Rainbow aura, also known as Titanium aura, is quartz that has been bonded with a thin layer of titanium, which creates an iridescent rainbow finish.

All of the quartz points have their own unique pattern and color layout.  The stones are fixed to bold, thick, gold chain, with an oversized lobster clasp.  The chain measures 18" long, and the quartz points are approximately 2.5" at the longest point.

name: Amethyst and Leather Choker
description: This bold choker is made with a sparkling chunk of raw amethyst, with a rainbow iridescent, ostrich embossed leather. The base to the choker is brass, and the width of the choker is approximately 1.25".

name: Dusk Necklace
description:
This necklace is made with titanium aura quartz points, and raw amethyst.  The Titanium aura stones get progressively longer toward the center, and are spaced with gorgeous chunks of amethyst.  The stones are strung from a matte silver wire rope.

The necklace measures 18" long and rests right below the collarbone.  The longest stone in the center is approximately 3" long.

name: Red Coral Earrings
description:
These earrings are made with bright red slices of coral, and are accented with a brass bead.  These earrings are elegant and bold.  

They measure approximately 2" long.

name: Raw Amethyst Point Necklace
description:
This necklace is made with a beautiful, deep purple, raw amethyst crystal point.

The amethyst has been strung from a gold and black toned, 24" link chain.

name: Amazonite Bracelet
description: This bracelet is made with rich, aqua green colored amazonite.  The color is completely natural.  The stones are accented by a single brass bead, and are strung from a copper link chain.

name: Fresh Water Pearl and Hammered Brass Earrings
description: These earrings are made from iridescent, rainbow, fresh water pearls, and hand hammered brass. The pearls show the most beautiful array of colors and the brass has been hammered into large, oblong hoops. The hoops measure approximately 3" long.

name: Raw Amethyst and Brass Necklace
description: This necklace is made from a gorgeous, one of a kind amethyst cluster. Each amethyst cluster will be unique with these necklaces, but each one will be equally beautiful. The amethyst cluster measures approximately 2" long and is attached to hand-hammered brass. The brass is strung from an 18" copper toned chain.

name: Turquoise Ankh Necklace
description: This interesting necklace is made with vibrant blue, genuine turquoise, an iridescent fresh water pearl, and a classic ankh.  The 3.5" long pendant is strung from an 18", thin gold plated chain.

name: Rainbow Pyramids Earrings
description:
These earrings are made from beautiful iridescent rainbow aura quartz and rainbow aura agate geodes.  Both stones are a bright iridescent, rainbow of colors, and the geodes are full of sparkling druzy crystals.

The earrings measure approximately 1.75" long.

name: Twin Hearts Necklace
description:
The Twin Hearts necklace is always there to remind you that life is incomplete without love.  This simple yet bold necklace is made with solid brass hardware, and neon pink, braided, genuine leather.  

The leather rope measures 18" long and rests right below the collarbone.

name: Heartless Necklace
description:
Be ready to face anything with the "Heartless" necklace, made of solid brass, and woven brass chain.  Chic and bad ass, just like you. 

Chain measures 18" long and rests right below the collarbone.

name: Striker Neon Green
description:
At all costs, protect ya neck.  The new "Striker" necklace will do just that.  One part danger, two parts style.

Made with a natural quartz point and brass hardware.  The rope is made with neon green, braided, genuine leather. Measures 18" long.

name: Fanger Neon Pink
description:
Don't hide your fangs.  The Fanger necklace is made with genuine agate stones, carved into these delightfully dangerous fangs.  The necklace also features brass hardware, and neon pink, braided, genuine leather.

The leather measures 18" long and the focal part of the necklace rests right below the collar bone.

name: Silver Druzy Teardrop Earrings
description:
These earrings are made with the most gorgeous titanium aura chalcedony stones. The chalcedony stones, which are covered in druzy crystals, have been coated in a thin layer of titanium, which gives it the vibrant silver color. This style is sweet and simple, yet very eye-catching.

The stones have been strung from sterling silver ear wires. The stones measure approximately .75" long.

name: Plum Druzy Teardrop Earrings
description:
These earrings are made from stunning, titanium coated, plum druzy stones. The pear shaped stone are completely covered in glistening druzy crystals, and the color is a rich plum color; perfect for the winter!

The stones measure approximately .5" wide and are strung from gold plated ear wires.

name: Gold Druzy Teardrop Earrings
description:
These earrings are made with the most gorgeous titanium aura chalcedony stones. The chalcedony stones, which are covered in druzy crystals, have been coated in a thin layer of titanium, which gives it the vibrant gold color. This style is sweet and simple, yet very eye-catching.

The stones have been strung from gold plated ear wires. The stones measure approximately .5" long.

name: Rainbow Druzy Teardrop Earrings
description:
These earrings are made with the most gorgeous titanium aura chalcedony stones. The chalcedony stones, which are covered in druzy crystals, have been coated in a thin layer of titanium, which gives it the vibrant, illustrious rainbow of colors. This style is sweet and simple, yet very eye-catching.

The stones have been strung from gold plated ear wires. The stones measure approximately .75" long.

name: Gold Moon Rock Heart Studs
description:
These sweet earrings are made from titanium aura quartz stones. Titanium aura quartz is formed when a thin layer of titanium is bonded with quartz crystals. The end result is this bright, gold color.

The stones are covered in sparkly druzy crystals that capture the light wonderfully! The hearts measure approximately 1/2" wide and are set on gold plated ear posts.

name: Black Tourmaline Vertebrae Earrings
description:
These elegant earrings are made with black tourmaline stones, and gold vertebrae chain. The tourmaline is a very rich, black color, with a smooth, velvety texture. The stones have been strung from a matte, gold toned, vertebrae chain.

The earrings measure approximately 4" long.

name: Pyrite Vertebrae Earrings
description:
These earrings are the perfect combination of natural beauty and modern edge.  They are made with a gold toned, vertebrae chain, and adorned with glistening pyrite druzy stones.

Each pyrite druzy stone is completely natural and will vary slightly from pair to pair.  Each one is covered in sparkling druzy crystals.  

Earrings measure approximately 3" long.

name: Amethyst Meteor Shower Earrings
description:
You will love these pretty, chic amethyst earrings! They are made from very high grade, faceted amethyst, and have been accented with glistening antique gold chain tassels. This style is so now, yet still timeless.

Earrings are strung from gold plated ear hooks and measure approximately 5" long.

name: Mystic Aura and Chain Earrings
description:
These stunners are made with a combination of pale purple, mystic aura quartz, tiny rainbow aura nuggets, and thick, antique gold chain.  These earrings are so on trend right now, combining galaxy, geometric and goddess trends all in one!

The earrings hang approximately 3".

name: Meteor Shower Earrings with Pyrite
description:
These classy, yet trendy earrings, are made with gorgeous pyrite on a quartz matrix. The stones have been adorned with antique gold toned, chain tassels. 

The pyrite glistens beautifully, as the stones are covered in druzy crystals. 

The earrings measure approximately 5" long.

name: Rings of Saturn Earrings with Pyrite
description:
You are going to turn some heads with these statement earrings! They are made from gorgeous pyrite, on a quartz matrix, and a combo of three different types of copper chain. The chains, which hang at three different lengths, are strung from ear to ear, creating a super modern look. 

The chains all rest right at the top of the chest.

name: Shooting Star Earrings
description: These fun, shooting star inspired earrings are made from gorgeous pyrite on a quartz matrix, as well as three different types of copper chain. The chains fall from the pyrite in a gradation of three lengths, with the longest measuring approximately 8" long.

name: Paua Shell Tassel Earrings
description:
The summer is made for the beach.  What better way to adorn your ears for this occasion, than a pair of glistening paua shell earrings.  Paua shells, also known as abalone, have a gorgeous, natural, rainbow pattern.  The shells have been modernized with gunmetal, chain tassels.  

The earrings hand approximately 4.5" long.

name: Purple Agate and Brass Cuff
description:
This cuff is made with the most eye-catching, purple agate stone. The agate is the most vibrant shade of purple, and the center of the stone is brimming with sparkly druzy crystals. 

The stone measures approximately 4" long, and is set on a 3"long, raw brass cuff. The cuff is very pliable and can be bent to fit most wrists.

name: Stellar Explosion Cuff~~Featured in Time Out New York
description:
Please note that due to the nature of the stones, each cuff will vary slightly, however you are guaranteed that it will be equally as beautiful. 

The cuff is a stellar explosion of pyrite, amethyst, angel aura quartz, and rainbow aura quartz.  The stones are set on a black leather backing, with a brass base.  The cuff is very pliable and will fit most wrists.

name: Titanium Aura Quartz Ring
description:
Please note that these rings are one of a kind and vary from piece to piece, however each one is equally beautiful.  

This ring is made with a stunning titanium aura quartz cluster. Titanium aura quartz is formed when titanium is permanently bonded with quartz crystals. The end result is the illustrious array of colors that you see here!

This particular cluster is so interesting and beautiful. The pattern of quartz crystals is gorgeous, and unique to this particular stone. There are also small pockets of druzy crystals that glisten on the stone.

The stone measures approximately 1.75" wide and is set on an adjustable ring.

name: Royal Aura Quartz and Leather Cuff
description:
This one of a kind cuff is made with a combination of a stunning, royal aura quartz stone, gold vertebrae chain, and cracked, metallic leather. Royal aura quartz is formed when a thin layer of titanium is bonded with clear quartz crystals. The end result is the illustrious blue color that you see here. 

The stone has been set on a pretty, metallic blue leather, with a crackled effect. The leather has been accented by gold vertebrae chain. 

Everything is set on a 1.5" brass cuff. The cuff will adjust to fit most wrists.

name: Isis Necklace
description:
The Isis necklace is named for Isis, the Egyptian Goddess.  Only a necklace that represents such regality, could carry her name.  You will love this piece made with hand dip dyed rope, in a purple and magenta ombre.  The center of the rope is adorned with five rainbow aura quartz stones, which are in vibrant hues of purple, pink, blue and green.

The necklace measures approximately 18" long.

name: Dark Matter Quartz and Brass Cuff
description:
**Please note the exact stone used for your bracelet will vary slightly. 

This cuff is made with a gorgeous royal aura quartz specimen. Royal aura quartz is made when titanium is permanently bonded with natural forming quartz crystal clusters. The end result is an illustrious array of blues, purples and gold.

It is set on a raw hammered brass cuff. The cuff is 1.5" at the widest point, and tapers f at the edges to a width of 1".

name: Royal Aura Quartz and Concave Brass Cuff
description:
This lovely cuff is made with a one of a kind, royal aura quartz stone. Royal aura is formed when a thin layer of titanium is bonded with clear quartz crystals, resulting in the vibrant blue color you see here. 

The stone has been set on a concave, raw brass cuff. The cuff is pliable and will fit most wrists. The cuff measures 1" wide.

name: Vintage Reflective Circular Sunglasses-Black RIm
description: These are authentic vintage sunglasses, circa the early 90's. These are new old stock, which means they are real vintage, but have never been worn before. This style was so big in the early 90's, and it is creeping back to a big comeback! The rims are black, and the lens's have a reflective rainbow quality. These sunglasses are in mint condition and will immediately send you through a 90's time warp!

name: Raw Amethyst Necklace
description:
This necklace is made from a lovely, raw chunk of amethyst, which has been strung from a thick, looped, gold tone chain. This style is simple, elegant, and naturally beautiful.

The chain measures 24" long, and the stone is approximately 1.5" wide.

name: Mystic Aura and Chain Necklace
description:
This necklace is made with a combination of pale purple, mystic aura quartz, tiny rainbow aura nuggets, and thick, antique gold chain.  This necklace is so on trend right now, combining galaxy, geometric and goddess trends all in one!

The chain measures 24" long.

name: Pyrite and Tourmaline Quartz Necklace
description:
This necklace is made with most gorgeous, glittering piece of pyrite, and a mellow, charcoal grey tourmaline quartz point. 

The pyrite is covered in glistening druzy crystals that sparkle brilliantly, and it is contrasted with the matte finish of the quartz. The stones are strung from a 24", thin, copper toned chain.
The pendant measures approximately 4" long. 

Would you like to switch your chain out with another one you see in my store? Would you like it longer? No problem, just ask!

name: ITEM OF THE DAY Freshwater Pearl and Chain Ring
description:
This ring is made with simple yet eye popping freshwater pearls.  The pearls have an iridescent oil slick finish, with a rainbow of colors.  The pearls are fixed to an antique gold tone chain.

This ring is available in any size you need.  Just specify your ring size in the checkout notes.  If no size is given, you will be given a size 7 as a default.

name: Fuchsia Agate and Brass Cuff
description:
This cuff is made with the most eye-catching, fuchsia agate stone. The agate is the most vibrant shade of fuchsia, and the center of the stone is brimming with sparkly druzy crystals. 

The stone measures approximately 3" long, and is set on a 2.5"long, raw brass cuff. The cuff is very pliable and can be bent to fit most wrists

name: Angel Aura Amethyst and Quartz Point Ring
description:
This one of a kind ring is made with angel aura quartz, amethyst, and clear quartz. The three stones come together to make the most amazing combination! Angel aura quartz is formed when zircon is bonded with clear quartz, resulting in the opalescent array of colors you see.

The tallest point is about 1.5" tall, and they are all set in a hammered, gold plated, adjustable ring.

name: Citrine Goddess Hand Harness
description:
You are going to fall in love with this hand harness, made with a gorgeous piece of citrine! The citrine is an intense orange color, and it is covered in sparkling crystals. The stone has been gold plated and is set on an adjustable ring. 

The stone is then connected to an intricately woven, brass chain. The chain then wraps around the wrist, and is attached with a lobster clasp. The bracelet is adjustable so it will fit most wrists.

name: Agate and Leather Hand Harness
description:
This is the first hand harness of it's kind! This combination ring and cuff bracelet is made with a vibrant orange and yellow agate stone, set on a vibrant purple leather cuff. The "ring" connects to an intricate, antique gold toned chain, which then connects to the agate. The agate is then embellished with extra chain on the end for a tassel-like effect. 

The leather is wrapped around a brass base, which makes this cuff very pliable. It fits very comfortably, and will grab so much attention. The cuff itself measures 2" wide.

name: Amethyst Citrine and Quartz Ring
description:
This ring is made from a gorgeous selection of amethyst, citrine, and clear quartz points. All of the stones come together to form an eye-catching, one of a kind statement ring. 

The stones have been set in a gold plated ring base, with brushed detailing. The ring is adjustable and will fit most fingers.

name: Neon and Purple Leather Cuff
description:
This cuff is the perfect blend of neon and bright purple leather! The cuff is made with gold chain, which has been carefully woven with neon, rainbow string. The woven chain has been set on a base of a pretty purple, genuine leather. The base for the cuff itself is brass, so it is adjustable. 

The width of the cuff measures 1.5" and it will fit most wrists.

name: Rainbow Aura Quartz and Snake Leather CUff
description:
This gorgeous, one of a kind cuff, is made with a rainbow aura quartz specimen and natural toned, snake embossed leather. Rainbow aura quartz is formed by bonding a thin layer of titanium with clear quartz crystals. The end result is the luminescent rainbow of colors you see here. 

The stone is set on beige and tan, snake embossed, genuine leather. The leather is wrapped on a 1.5", 24Karat gold plate cuff. The cuff is very pliable and will fit most wrists.

name: Deep Space Gold Plated Amethyst Ring
description:
Please note, this ring is made to order, so the exact crystal formations vary slightly from ring to ring; however, each one will always be as beautiful as the first!

This ring is made with a gold plated, hammered ring, and several pretty purple chunks of amethyst. The amethyst is made up of of several hand selected chunks and has been bezel set, and is atop an extremely sturdy adjustable ring. This piece is fun, chic, and eye catching.

The ring measures approximately 1.25" wide and is adjustable.

The quartz is strung from a 30" long chain. The pendant itself measures approximately 5" long.

name: Royal Aura Quartz Gold Plated Cuff
description:
This cuff is made with a gorgeous, one of a kind, royal aura quartz stone. Royal aura quartz is formed by bonding a thin layer of titanium with clear quartz crystals. The end result is the beautiful array of royal blues and purple you see here. 

The stone is set on a 1.5" wide, 24 Karat gold plated cuff. The cuff is very pliable and will fit most wrists.

name: Meteor Shower Pyrite Tassel Necklace

The neon rope has been intricately woven into the matte gold fishbone chain, and it pops vibrantly! It is contrasted nicely with the textured, pretty black tourmaline stone. This piece perfectly merges contemporary edge with natural beauty. 

The necklace measures approximately 30" long.

name: Quartz and Chain Body Armor
description:
Protect your style this season with full body armor jewelry.  This piece is made with heat-treated quartz, resulting in an opalescent finish.  The stones are intricately strung amid layers of chain and brass adornments.

The chains are all adjustable, and are attached around the back with lobster clasps.

name: Stellar Explosion Purple Leather Cuff
description: The cuff is a stellar explosion of pyrite, amethyst, angel aura quartz, and rainbow aura quartz. The stones are set on a genuine purple leather backing, with a brass base. The cuff is very pliable and will fit most wrists. The cuff measures 2" wide.

name: Gold Plated Mixed Quartz Ring Version 2
description:
This statement ring is made with a mixture of clear quartz, amethyst, and titanium aura quartz. All of the stones work together to create a true stunner of a ring, with a rainbow of hues. 

The stones are bezel set on a gold plated, hammered, adjustable ring. The stones are about 1.5" at the tallest point.

This statement ring is made with a mixture of clear quartz, amethyst, citrine, and titanium aura quartz. All of the stones work together to create a true stunner of a ring, with a rainbow of hues. 

The stones are bezel set on a gold plated, hammered, adjustable ring. The stones are about 1.5" at the tallest point.

name: Mystic Aura Goddess Headdress
description:
This exquisite headdress will have you feeling like a goddess! It is made with two different types of antique gold tone chain, and pale purple mystic quartz. The quartz gets its pale purple color from being bonded with a thin layer of titanium. 

The headdress is adjustable and will therefor fit anyone! Feel free to request a different type of stone if you like, such as pyrite.

description:

name: Raw Pyrite Cluster Ring
description:
Pyrite, also known as fool's gold, is a natural mineral.  It comes in many different forms, such as pyrite cubes, pyrite blossoms, and pyrite sand dollars to name a few.  These stones glimmer so brilliantly and are great statement pieces!

Each stone has been hand selected for its beauty and originality.  Each one is one of a kind.  The ring pictured here is representative of the typical quality and look, however you will not be receiving this exact stone.  It is impossible for two stones to be exactly the same since these are formed by nature, however you have my guarantee that each ring is equally beautiful!

The stone measures approximately 1.5" wide and is set on an antique brass colored adjustable ring.
